thread.title: EuroMillions results live: Winning numbers for Tuesday, December 4 with a £51m jackpot - Devon Live

author: Jamie Hawkins
title: EuroMillions results live: Winning numbers for Tuesday, December 4 with a £51m jackpot - Devon Live
text:
Euromillions numbers (Image: Johnny Green/PA Wire)
An incredible £51m is up for grabs in tonight's Euromillions draw.
The winning numbers will be drawn tonight at 8.40pm - and we'll be covering it live.
Mortgage worries most likely over, if you win the Euromillions you could have your holiday of a lifetime this summer, and live like a king or queen (at least for a while).
Scroll down to our live blog where the numbers will be drawn live. Read More Brexit is good news for Euromillions Lottery players but only if you win the jackpot
Players of EuroMillions are also given an automatic entry into the UK Millionaire Maker - where they must match with a drawn code.
A EuroMillions ticket costs £2.50 and players must select five numbers from 1-50 and two lucky star numbers from 1-12.
Fancy boosting you chances? Players can play up to seven lines of numbers on each pay slip and buy 10 slips at a time.
You can play up to four weeks in advance and ticket sales close at 7:30pm - around an hour before EuroMillions draw on Tuesdays and Fridays.
Check back here later for the full set of EuroMillions results, as well as Millionaire Maker codes, in our live coverage of the draw below. 21:01
Remember there’s an incredible £51m up for grabs. Is tonight your lucky night? 20:59 EuroMillions draw for Tuesday, December 4
Tonight’s winning numbers are 19, 20, 21, 42 and 45.
The lucky stars are 8 and 9. 20:57 And the results are in! More On
